subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Hendrick Motorsports said Friday that contractual commitments to the team’s current sponsors would preclude Budweiser as the primary sponsor of Dale Earnhardt Jr.’s car.
